pullRequest.title: [BEAM-10562]Eliminate nullability errors from :sdks:java:extensions:join-library
pullRequest.bodyText:
This enables the checker analyzer in the join-library extension, preventing nullability errors in this module.
I found nullability issues only in the testing code and which were expected for the test-case purposes, hence I have suppressed them
